      "content": "Wait, \"just a figure\"? That's a bit worrying. If I pass a 90% confidence rating to the client and it turns out you were just guessing based on \"intuition\" rather than actual data, it's my neck on the line. Are you saying there isn't actually enough verifiable intel to back up that 90% number? I need to know if I'm presenting them with a fact or a feeling.",
